<DOCUMENT>
  <ParallelChunk annotation_id="0" docOffset="0">
    <en>8.</en>
    <fr>8.</fr>
  </ParallelChunk>
<ParallelChunk annotation_id="3" docOffset="1">
    <en>Nuclear non-proliferation and disarmament (vote)</en>
    <fr>Non-prolifération <DiscourseConnective annotation_id="21">et</DiscourseConnective> désarmement nucléaires (vote)</fr>
  </ParallelChunk>
<ParallelChunk annotation_id="52" docOffset="2">
    <en>- Before the vote:</en>
    <fr>
      <DiscourseConnective annotation_id="54">Avant</DiscourseConnective> le vote:</fr>
  </ParallelChunk>
<Speaker annotation_id="71" id="116" name="Monica Frassoni">
    <ParallelChunk annotation_id="71" docOffset="3">
      <en>(IT) Mr President, my group made a mistake in not asking in time for two votes to be taken by roll call.</en>
      <fr>(IT) Monsieur le Président, mon groupe a commis l'erreur de ne pas avoir demandé <DiscourseConnective annotation_id="150">à</DiscourseConnective> temps <DiscourseConnective annotation_id="158">que</DiscourseConnective> deux votes soient effectués par appel nominal.</fr>
    </ParallelChunk>
<ParallelChunk annotation_id="176" docOffset="4">
      <en>
        <Alignment alignment="209" annotation_id="176">
          <DiscourseConnective annotation_id="176" sense="Contingency.Condition">If</DiscourseConnective>
        </Alignment> there are no objections, I should like to ask you kindly to authorise us to do so now, even <Alignment alignment="339" annotation_id="271">
          <DiscourseConnective annotation_id="271" sense="Comparison.Contrast">though</DiscourseConnective>
        </Alignment> we have missed the deadline.</en>
      <fr>
        <Alignment alignment="1098" annotation_id="209">
          <DiscourseConnective annotation_id="209" sense="Contingency.Condition">Si</DiscourseConnective>
        </Alignment> vous n'y voyez pas d'objection, je voudrais vous demander aimablement de nous autoriser <DiscourseConnective annotation_id="300">à</DiscourseConnective> introduire cette demande <DiscourseConnective annotation_id="327">maintenant</DiscourseConnective>, <Alignment alignment="271" annotation_id="339">
          <DiscourseConnective annotation_id="339" sense="Comparison.Contrast">même si</DiscourseConnective>
        </Alignment> nous avons dépassé le délai.</fr>
    </ParallelChunk>
<ParallelChunk annotation_id="307" docOffset="5">
      <en>In the original text, it would affect paragraph 1, second part of the split vote that is on the voting list, and paragraph 9, again in the original text, where voting on separate parts is provided for: we request a vote by roll call in this case as well, <Alignment alignment="649" annotation_id="562">
          <DiscourseConnective annotation_id="562" sense="Contingency.Condition">if</DiscourseConnective>
        </Alignment> you agree and will kindly forgive us for the mistake we have made.</en>
      <fr>Dans le texte original, cela concernerait le paragraphe 1, deuxième partie du vote par division figurant sur la liste de vote, <DiscourseConnective annotation_id="503">et</DiscourseConnective> le paragraphe 9, toujours du texte original, qui prévoit un vote par division: nous demandons également un vote par appel nominal <DiscourseConnective annotation_id="636">dans ce cas</DiscourseConnective>, <Alignment alignment="562" annotation_id="649">
          <DiscourseConnective annotation_id="649" sense="Contingency.Condition">si</DiscourseConnective>
        </Alignment> vous êtes d'accord <DiscourseConnective annotation_id="671">et</DiscourseConnective> si vous voulez bien nous pardonner l'erreur que nous avons commise.</fr>
    </ParallelChunk>
<ParallelChunk annotation_id="632" docOffset="6">
      <en>(Parliament agreed to the request)</en>
      <fr>(Le Parlement marque son accord)</fr>
    </ParallelChunk>
<ParallelChunk annotation_id="667" docOffset="7">
      <en>- Before the vote on paragraph 2:</en>
      <fr>
        <DiscourseConnective annotation_id="775">Avant</DiscourseConnective> le vote sur le paragraphe 2:</fr>
    </ParallelChunk>
</Speaker>
  <Speaker annotation_id="701" id="118" name="Vytautas Landsbergis">
    <ParallelChunk annotation_id="701" docOffset="8">
      <en>Mr President, we can improve paragraph 2 by adding only a few words.</en>
      <fr>(EN) Monsieur le Président, nous pouvons améliorer le paragraphe 2 <DiscourseConnective annotation_id="877">en</DiscourseConnective> y ajoutant quelques mots.</fr>
    </ParallelChunk>
<ParallelChunk annotation_id="770" docOffset="9">
      <en>It concerns our 'call on all States not part of the NPT to accede to that Treaty'.</en>
      <fr>Concernant le passage: "invite tous les États qui ne sont pas parties au TNP <DiscourseConnective annotation_id="983">à</DiscourseConnective> y adhérer".</fr>
    </ParallelChunk>
<ParallelChunk annotation_id="853" docOffset="10">
      <en>That is regular and routine.</en>
      <fr>Il <DiscourseConnective annotation_id="1000">s'</DiscourseConnective>agit d'une formulation d'usage courante.</fr>
    </ParallelChunk>
<ParallelChunk annotation_id="882" docOffset="11">
      <en>
        <Alignment alignment="1043" annotation_id="882">
          <DiscourseConnective annotation_id="882" sense="Comparison.Contrast">However</DiscourseConnective>
        </Alignment>, we could call on them first to 'comply voluntarily with', and <Alignment alignment="1122" annotation_id="953">
          <DiscourseConnective annotation_id="953" sense="Temporal.Asynchronous.Precedence">then</DiscourseConnective>
        </Alignment> to accede to, the Treaty, <Alignment alignment="1141" annotation_id="984">
          <DiscourseConnective annotation_id="984" sense="Contingency.Cause.Result">thus</DiscourseConnective>
        </Alignment> introducing fresh encouragement.</en>
      <fr>
        <Alignment alignment="297" annotation_id="1043">
          <DiscourseConnective annotation_id="1043" sense="Comparison.Contrast">Néanmoins</DiscourseConnective>
        </Alignment>, nous pourrions <DiscourseConnective annotation_id="1069">d'abord</DiscourseConnective> les inviter <DiscourseConnective annotation_id="1089">à</DiscourseConnective> "s'y conformer volontairement" <Alignment alignment="953" annotation_id="1122">
          <DiscourseConnective annotation_id="1122" sense="Temporal.Asynchronous.Precedence">avant d'</DiscourseConnective>
        </Alignment>y adhérer, <Alignment alignment="984" annotation_id="1141">
          <DiscourseConnective annotation_id="1141" sense="Contingency.Cause.Result">de manière à</DiscourseConnective>
        </Alignment> les y encourager.</fr>
    </ParallelChunk>
<ParallelChunk annotation_id="1022" docOffset="12">
      <en>(Parliament accepted the oral amendment)</en>
      <fr>(Le parlement adopte l'amendement oral)</fr>
    </ParallelChunk>
</Speaker>
  <Speaker annotation_id="1063" id="120" name="President">
    <ParallelChunk annotation_id="1063" docOffset="13">
      <en>That concludes the vote.</en>
      <fr>Le vote est clos.</fr>
    </ParallelChunk>
</Speaker>
</DOCUMENT>
